   <div id="content"> 
    <h2>Westmont College Prospect Camps </h2> 
    <p> Westmont College Athletics offers Prospect Camps to high school student athletes looking to develop in their sport. Players will get to work with Westmont College Head Coaches, Assistant Coaches and student-athletes (prior and current). If you want to play a collegiate sport and you think you have what it takes, this is the camp for you! Many college athletes are first seen at camps and it’s a great way to begin a relationship with our coaches, live like Westmont Athletes do on campus and learn what it means to be a part of the Westmont Community. Not only will these camps allow you to showcase your skills in front of Head Coaches it will also give you a taste of what collegiate athletics are all about on one of the most beautiful campuses in the country. <br> <br> </p> 
    <p><img src="images/sbmountains.jpg" alt="Santa Barbara hills"></p> 
    <p><strong>WHY OUR CAMPS?</strong></p> 
    <p> </p>
    <ul> 
     <li> Work daily with Westmont College Coaches and current and former players.</li> 
     <li> Train and play at one of the most beautiful campuses in the country in Santa Barbara, Ca and use the same facilities that host Westmont’s student-athletes.</li> 
     <li> Residential campers will stay in the dorms our students stay in during the school year- so you get the full Westmont experience!</li> 
     <li> Excellent trainers, supervision and camper to staff ratio.</li> 
     <li> Gear for all campers!</li> 
    </ul> 
    <p>Thanks for your interest in our camps- We hope to see you this summer!</p> 
